  PRD["<b>PRD</b><br/>what"] -->|SA + AI| SRS
  SRS["<b>SRS</b><br/>OpenAPI · spec · DB schema"] -->|QA + AI| QA
  QA["<b>QA cases 1~∞</b><br/>可跑驗收 · covers Rn"] --> RD
  RD["<b>RD-Agent</b><br/>開發 + 測試<br/>Code → CICD"] --> GATE

  subgraph GATE["DoD 閘門牆 — RD 通過 SA/QA 邊界"]
    direction TB
    G1["① Contract · OpenAPI snapshot"]
    G2["② Schema · entity ↔ DB"]
    G3["③ verify-c0 · 結構 / 只新增"]
    G4["④ QA 驗收 · 跑 QA cases"]
    G5["⑤ 覆蓋率 · ID 對表"]
    G6["⑥ Build 綠"]
    G7["⑦ LLM 語意審查 · advisory"]
    G1 ~~~ G2 ~~~ G3 ~~~ G4 ~~~ G5 ~~~ G6 ~~~ G7
  end

  GATE -->|①–⑥ 全綠| Done["✅ Done"]
  GATE -.->|❌ FAIL → 修，重跑| RD
  Done --> Issue["Issue<br/>bug → 回歸 case"]
  Issue -.->|新 QA case · 回歸 1~∞| QA

  SRS -. 定義 ①②③ .-> GATE
  QA  -. 定義 ④⑤ .-> GATE

